(86, 1, '2025-10-01 17:52:16', '2025-10-01 17:52:16', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Set in the town of Derry, Maine, the story follows a group of children (later revisited as adults) who band together to confront a shape-shifting creature that often takes the form of Pennywise the Dancing Clown. The novel explores themes of childhood trauma, fear, memory, and the enduring power of friendship.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'IT', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'it', '', '', '2025-10-02 01:37:54', '2025-10-02 01:37:54', '', 0, 'https://brehak.bitlampsites.com/wpd/final/?post_type=book&#038;p=86', 0, 'book', '', 0),
(87, 1, '2025-10-01 17:52:31', '2025-10-01 17:52:31', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Jack Torrance takes a job as the winter caretaker of the isolated Overlook Hotel, bringing along his wife Wendy and his young son Danny, who has psychic abilities known as the shining. As snow traps them inside, the hotels malevolent forces prey on Jacks fragile mind, driving him toward violence. A classic tale of madness and supernatural terror.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'The Shining', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'the-shining', '', '', '2025-10-02 01:44:09', '2025-10-02 01:44:09', '', 0, 'https://brehak.bitlampsites.com/wpd/final/?post_type=book&#038;p=87', 0, 'book', '', 0),
(88, 1, '2025-10-01 17:53:24', '2025-10-01 17:53:24', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The Creed family moves to a new home in Maine, near a mysterious burial ground with the power to bring the dead back to life. When tragedy strikes, Dr. Louis Creed makes a desperate choice that unleashes horrifying consequences. A chilling exploration of grief, death, and the cost of tampering with nature.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Pet Sematary', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'pet-sematary', '', '', '2025-10-02 01:42:09', '2025-10-02 01:42:09', '', 0, 'https://brehak.bitlampsites.com/wpd/final/?post_type=book&#038;p=88', 0, 'book', '', 0),
(89, 1, '2025-10-01 17:53:44', '2025-10-01 17:53:44', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>A psychological horror novel about Jessie Burlingame, who becomes trapped handcuffed to a bed in a remote cabin after her husband dies suddenly during a game gone wrong. Isolated and immobilized, she must face not only her dire physical situation but also haunting memories and a possible intruder lurking in the shadows.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Geralds Game', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'geralds-game', '', '', '2025-10-02 01:36:07', '2025-10-02 01:36:07', '', 0, 'https://brehak.bitlampsites.com/wpd/final/?post_type=book&#038;p=89', 0, 'book', '', 0),
(90, 1, '2025-10-01 17:53:56', '2025-10-01 17:53:56', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>After a car accident, novelist Paul Sheldon is rescued by Annie Wilkes, his number one fan. But Annies devotion turns sinister when she discovers Paul has killed off her favorite character. Holding him captive, she forces him to write a new novel under terrifying conditions. A tense story of obsession, captivity, and survival.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Misery', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'misery', '', '', '2025-10-02 01:40:06', '2025-10-02 01:40:06', '', 0, 'https://brehak.bitlampsites.com/wpd/final/?post_type=book&#038;p=90', 0, 'book', '', 0),
