(118, 1, '2025-10-06 15:03:53', '2025-10-06 15:03:53', '<!-- wp:columns -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns\"><!-- wp:column {\"width\":\"33.33%\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\" style=\"flex-basis:33.33%\"><!-- wp:image {\"id\":56,\"width\":\"277px\",\"height\":\"auto\",\"sizeSlug\":\"full\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full is-resized\"><img src=\"https://brehak.bitlampsites.com/wpd/final/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/1.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-56\" style=\"width:277px;height:auto\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column {\"width\":\"66.66%\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\" style=\"flex-basis:66.66%\"><!-- wp:heading {\"textAlign\":\"center\",\"style\":{\"typography\":{\"fontStyle\":\"italic\",\"fontWeight\":\"800\"}}} -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading has-text-align-center\" style=\"font-style:italic;font-weight:800\">\"Here\'s Johnny!\"</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The&nbsp;purpose&nbsp;of&nbsp;this&nbsp;website&nbsp;is&nbsp;to&nbsp;honor&nbsp;and&nbsp;recognize&nbsp;the&nbsp;impact&nbsp;that Stephen&nbsp;King&nbsp;has&nbsp;made&nbsp;to&nbsp;horror&nbsp;fans&nbsp;across&nbsp;all&nbsp;genres.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Stephen&nbsp;King&nbsp;creates&nbsp;a&nbsp;book&nbsp;for&nbsp;everyone,&nbsp;whether&nbsp;they&nbsp;are&nbsp;seasoned&nbsp;horror&nbsp;fans&nbsp;or&nbsp;more&nbsp;recent&nbsp;viewers&nbsp;just&nbsp;getting&nbsp;started. He&nbsp;basically&nbsp;established&nbsp;an&nbsp;expected&nbsp;image&nbsp;for&nbsp;himself&nbsp;by&nbsp;breaking&nbsp;the&nbsp;rules&nbsp;of&nbsp;horror.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Knowing&nbsp;a&nbsp;lot&nbsp;about&nbsp;what&nbsp;you&nbsp;do&nbsp;is&nbsp;one&nbsp;thing,&nbsp;but&nbsp;becoming&nbsp;an&nbsp;expert&nbsp;in&nbsp;it&nbsp;and&nbsp;showing&nbsp;the&nbsp;world&nbsp;your&nbsp;talent&nbsp;has&nbsp;left&nbsp;horror&nbsp;lovers&nbsp;of&nbsp;all&nbsp;ages&nbsp;and&nbsp;types&nbsp;with&nbsp;amazing&nbsp;memories&nbsp;for&nbsp;decades.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>On this website, you can browse and read the author\'s biography, as well as visit the books page, which includes details on the publisher, publication date, number of pages, and total cost of his well-known book collection.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Reviews and a brief overview of the book\'s subject matter, along with the factors that influenced Stephen\'s writing, will also be included.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Lastly, there is a contact page where you can email Stephen directly or offer advice.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns -->\n\n<!-- wp:columns -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns\"><!-- wp:column {\"width\":\"25%\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\" style=\"flex-basis:25%\"><!-- wp:image {\"id\":59,\"sizeSlug\":\"full\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\",\"className\":\"is-style-default\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full is-style-default\"><img src=\"https://brehak.bitlampsites.com/wpd/final/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/14853840-L-e1759330951919.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-59\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column {\"width\":\"50%\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\" style=\"flex-basis:50%\"><!-- wp:group {\"fontSize\":\"medium\",\"layout\":{\"type\":\"constrained\"}} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-group has-medium-font-size\"><!-- wp:heading {\"textAlign\":\"center\",\"style\":{\"typography\":{\"fontStyle\":\"italic\",\"fontWeight\":\"800\"}}} -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading has-text-align-center\" style=\"font-style:italic;font-weight:800\">Think Like a KING!</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"align\":\"center\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\">\"Get busy living or get busy dying\".</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"align\":\"center\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\">\"We make up horrors to help us cope with the real ones\".</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"align\":\"center\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\">\"Monsters are real, and ghosts are real too. They live inside us, and sometimes, they win\".</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"align\":\"center\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\">\"Books are a uniquely portable magic\".&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"align\":\"center\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\">\"Fiction is the truth inside the lie\".</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"align\":\"center\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\">\"Love isn\'t soft, like those poets say. Love has teeth which bite and the wounds never close.\"&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"align\":\"center\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\">\"No one can tell what goes on in between the person you were and the person you become\"&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n<!-- /wp:group --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column {\"width\":\"25%\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\" style=\"flex-basis:25%\"><!-- wp:image {\"id\":60,\"sizeSlug\":\"full\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\",\"className\":\"is-style-default\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full is-style-default\"><img src=\"https://brehak.bitlampsites.com/wpd/final/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/14853840-L-1-e1759330979515.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-60\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns -->\n\n<!-- wp:block {\"ref\":117} /-->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Welcome', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '2-revision-v1', '', '', '2025-10-06 15:03:53', '2025-10-06 15:03:53', '', 2, 'https://brehak.bitlampsites.com/wpd/final/?p=118', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(119, 1, '2025-10-06 15:05:37', '2025-10-06 15:05:37', '<!-- wp:columns -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns\"><!-- wp:column {\"width\":\"33.33%\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\" style=\"flex-basis:33.33%\"></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column {\"width\":\"66.66%\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\" style=\"flex-basis:66.66%\"><!-- wp:heading {\"textAlign\":\"center\",\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading has-text-align-center\"><strong>Fan Mail &amp; Letters</strong></h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"align\":\"left\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-text-align-left\">Fans are welcome to send letters to Stephen King at his official mailing address:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><em>Stephen King</em><br>P.O. Box 666<br>SomeCity, ME 12345<br>USA</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>(Please note: Due to the large volume of mail he receives, individual replies are not guaranteed.)<br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"textAlign\":\"center\",\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading has-text-align-center\"><strong>Publisher Inquiries</strong></h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>For questions related to Stephen Kings books, publishing rights, or translations, please contact his U.S. publisher:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><em>Scribner / Simon &amp; Schuster</em><br>1230 Avenue of the Americas<br>New York, NY 10020</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"textAlign\":\"center\",\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading has-text-align-center\">Stay Connected with the KING!</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Stephen King is active on social media and often posts updates and thoughts directly to his readers. You can follow him on:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li><a href=\"https://twitter.com/stephenking\">Twitter</a></li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li><a>Official Website</a></li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns -->\n\n<!-- wp:block {\"ref\":117} /-->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Contact Us', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '39-revision-v1', '', '', '2025-10-06 15:05:37', '2025-10-06 15:05:37', '', 39, 'https://brehak.bitlampsites.com/wpd/final/?p=119', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
